s of the feet. Then reflexology treatment and foot massage. We then finish with your choice of either grapefruit tangerine or vanilla mint sugar scrub. Salt can dehydrate the skin. That\'s why we make our foot scrubs with sugar. Its naturally hydrating properties soothe and smooth your skin for a more refreshing experience. Smooth and hydrate your feet while relieving foot pain and discomfort.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"btn\">Book</a>\r\n\r\nPricing\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Foot Massage- $30</li>\r\n 	<li>60 minutes - $70</li>\r\n 	<li>90 minutes - $100</li>\r\n 	<li>120 minutes - $120</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_color=\"#171617\" inertia=\"0.1\" padding=\"0 0 110px\" margin_bottom=\"0\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 72px;\"><a name=\"our_work\"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"big-headline\" style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: 300;\">About</h2>\r\nSteven Wunder\r\n\r\nPhoto (Name and title under photo)\r\n\r\nI believe that you can only change someones health and ultimately their quality of life through education and empowerment. With the aid of soft tissue manipulation (massage) and proper lifestyle you can achieve and maintain a state of balance and efficiency of systems known as homeostasis. The neurological reset that massage gives you allows your body to rest and restore itself the way it is designed to.\r\n\r\nI approach massage as a teacher. I educate my clients on how to improve their neuromuscular health and give them the knowledge they need to avoid dysfunction and maintain the progress made during treatment.\r\n\r\nWHY MASSAGE?\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Because it works, plain and simple. Massage has been used for thousands of years to treat injury, relieve stress and promote health. You do it yourself and dont even know it. If you bump your arm on the table your first subconscious act it to rub where it hurts.</li>\r\n 	<li>There have been study after study and they all have the same result. The best way relieve hypertonicity (tension) of a muscle is through physical manipulation. I have seen it time and time again, one hour on the table can do you a world of good. Come and let us make a believer out of you.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAmy Whittle\r\n\r\nPhoto (Name and title under photo)\r\n\r\nPhilosophy: We are all creatures of habit. With habits come repetitive motion, behaviors and stressors in our minds and bodies. Throughout time this will manifest through muscular pain and imbalances in our physical body and fatigue, irritation and stress in our mental and emotional bodies; resulting in a decreased productivity, functionality and appetite for living life. To create a balance in the physical body will allow us to also create a balanced and calm mind allowing all your bodies to seamlessly interconnect and function at your bodies peak.\r\n\r\nTechniques practiced\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Active Isolated Stretching</li>\r\n 	<li>Deep Tissue massage</li>\r\n 	<li>Myofascial release</li>\r\n 	<li>Neuromuscular</li>\r\n 	<li>Orthopedic Massage</li>\r\n 	<li>Reflexology</li>\r\n 	<li>Reiki</li>\r\n 	<li>Sports Massage</li>\r\n 	<li>Thai Massage</li>\r\n 	<li>Trigger Point therapy</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding=\"0 0 110px\" inertia=\"0.1\" margin_bottom=\"0\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 72px;\"><a name=\"services\"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"big-headline\" style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: 300;\">Blog</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_color=\"#171617\" padding=\"0 0 110px\" inertia=\"0.1\" margin_bottom=\"0\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[blog-grid-rows]\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 72px;\"><a name=\"clients\"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"big-headline\" style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: 300;\">Contact</h2>\r\nRequest Your Appointment\r\n\r\nWe will contact you shortly to confirm your appointment (smaller font)\r\n[contact_form]\r\nMap on opposite side with address below\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding=\"30px 0 20px\" margin_bottom=\"0\" inertia=\"0.1\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Copyright  2016W Massage and Wellness</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]", "One Page - Portfolio", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "4924-revision-v1", "", "", "2016-08-13 01:29:23", "2016-08-13 01:29:23", "", "4924", "http://localhost:8888/wordpress/2016/08/13/4924-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
