INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("6346", "1", "2016-09-07 16:31:02", "2016-09-08 00:31:02", "&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 48px;\"><a name=\"about_us\"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"big-headline\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #717073;\">Services</h2>\r\nAt W. Massage &amp; Wellness in Atlanta, we offer a variety of massage treatments that can be custom blended to suit your specific needs.\r\n\r\n<section class=\"services-section\">\r\n<div class=\"one\">\r\n<div class=\"services-text\">Swedish</div>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6239\" src=\"https://www.puretopiancreative.com/wmassage/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/w-massage-swedish.jpg\" alt=\"w-massage-swedish\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"two\">Swedish massage is the most common massage modality. Your therapist will use gliding strokes, circular pressure, kneading percussive strokes to relax your entire body as well as improve circulation and ease tension.\r\n<a class=\"btn\">Book</a></div>\r\n</section><section class=\"services-section\">\r\n<div class=\"one\">\r\n<div class=\"services-text-dt\" style=\"line-height: 1em;\">Deep Tissue /NMT</div>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6234\" src=\"https://www.puretopiancreative.com/wmassage/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/w-massage-deep-tissue.jpg\" alt=\"w-massage-deep-tissue\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"two\">This modality uses deeper, more specific stokes and static pressure to target individual muscles or muscle groups. These techniques can help to elevate pain and discomfort caused by chronic tension, adhesions (when the layers of tissue get stuck together) or trigger points.\r\n<a class=\"btn\">Book</a></div>\r\n</section><section class=\"services-section\">\r\n<div class=\"one\">\r\n<div class=\"services-text\">Sports</div>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6237\" src=\"https://www.puretopiancreative.com/wmassage/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/w-massage-sports.jpg\" alt=\"w-massage-sports\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"two\">Sports massage is geared towards athletes and can be focused to a specific sport. It is designed to target overused or stressed muscles, ligaments and joints to help elevate soreness, improve flexibility and range of motion and help avoid injury during training.\r\n<a class=\"btn\">Book</a></div>\r\n</section><section class=\"services-section\">\r\n<div class=\"one\">\r\n<div class=\"services-text\">Thai</div>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6246\" src=\"https://www.puretopiancreative.com/wmassage/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/w-massage-thai.jpg\" alt=\"w-massage-thai\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"two\">Therapist apply pressure along Zen lines using their hands, knees, feet and body weight to stimulate energy in the body, in addition move and stretch the client in and out of yoga postures with a Thai chi like flow. The Client is encouraged to not assist or resist, therefore receiving many of the benefits of yoga effortlessly.\r\n<a class=\"btn\">Book</a></div>\r\n</section><section class=\"services-section-foot\">\r\n<div class=\"one-foot\">\r\n<div class=\"services-text\">Foot</div>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6235\" src=\"https://www.puretopiancreative.com/wmassage/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/w-massage-foot.jpg\" alt=\"w-massage-foot\" width=\"200\" height=\"150\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"two-foot\">Treat your feet to 30 minutes of bliss. With our foot massage and sugar scrub. Starting with hot towels to sooth and relax the muscles of the feet. Then reflexology treatment and foot massage. We then finish with your choice of either grapefruit tangerine or vanilla mint sugar scrub. Salt can dehydrate the skin. That\'s why we make our foot scrubs with sugar. Its naturally hydrating properties soothe and smooth your skin for a more refreshing experience. Smooth and hydrate your feet while relieving foot pain and discomfort.\r\n<a class=\"btn\">Book</a></div>\r\n</section>Pricing\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Foot Massage- $30</li>\r\n 	<li>60 minutes - $70</li>\r\n 	<li>90 minutes - $100</li>\r\n 	<li>120 minutes - $120</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_color=\"#299ca8\" inertia=\"0.1\" padding=\"0 0 110px\" margin_bottom=\"0\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 72px;\"><a name=\"our_work\"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"big-headline\" style=\"text-align: left; color: white;\">About</h2>\r\n<section style=\"color: white;\">\r\n<div style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-6238 profile\" src=\"https://www.puretopiancreative.com/wmassage/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/w-massage-steven.jpg\" alt=\"w-massage-steven\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />\r\nSteven Wunder\r\nOwner</div>\r\nI believe that you can only change someones health and ultimately their quality of life through education and empowerment. With the aid of soft tissue manipulation (massage) and proper lifestyle you can achieve and maintain a state of balance and efficiency of systems known as homeostasis. The neurological reset that massage gives you allows your body to rest and restore itself the way it is designed to.\r\n\r\nI approach massage as a teacher. I educate my clients on how to improve their neuromuscular health and give them the knowledge they need to avoid dysfunction and maintain the progress made during treatment.\r\n\r\nWHY MASSAGE?\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Because it works, plain and simple. Massage has been used for thousands of years to treat injury, relieve stress and promote health. You do it yourself and dont even know it. If you bump your arm on the table your first subconscious act it to rub where it hurts.</li>\r\n 	<li>There have been study after study and they all have the same result. The best way relieve hypertonicity (tension) of a muscle is through physical manipulation. I have seen it time and time again, one hour on the table can do you a world of good. Come and let us make a believer out of you.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n</section><section>[vc_row bg_color=\"#dad9d9\" padding=\"0 0 110px\" inertia=\"0.1\" margin_bottom=\"0\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 72px;\"><a name=\"services\"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"big-headline\" style=\"text-align: left; color: #717073;\">Blog</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[vc_row bg_color=\"#dad9d9\" padding=\"0 0 110px\" inertia=\"0.1\" margin_bottom=\"0\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n\r\n[vc_row][vc_column][blog posts_per_page=\"4\" template=\"grid-rows\" columns=\"2\" post_excerpts=\"true\" excerpt_length=\"25\" image_width=\"600\" image_height=\"350\" tag_slug__in=\"standard\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n</section><section style=\"color: white;\">[vc_row bg_color=\"#299ca8\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<p style=\"padding-top: 72px;\"><a name=\"clients\"></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"big-headline\" style=\"text-align: left; color: white;\">Contact</h2>\r\nRequest Your Appointment\r\n\r\nWe will contact you shortly to confirm your appointment\r\n[contact_form]\r\n\r\n<iframe class=\"profile-map\" style=\"border: 0;\" src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3311.6143495771926!2d-84.38218118513703!3d33.89958473320761!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x88f50ee68cfdbcb1%3A0x317aa32f68c66220!2sW+Massage+%26+Wellness!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1471054152853\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r\nW. Massage &amp; Wellness\r\n5299 Roswell Rd suite 128\r\nAtlanta, GA 30342\r\nPhone: (404) 432-1631\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[vc_row bg_color=\"#299ca8\" padding=\"30px 0 20px\" margin_bottom=\"0\" inertia=\"0.1\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n</section>", "W Massage Home", "